{"tid":1102871,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"(音樂/心事台) 召集一眾巴絲入嚟傾計","createTime":"2019-04-12T04:27:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-13T04:44:11.000Z","uid":43718,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0090003227acc63aa3b2c15f6c5330e2ffa6c638","tid":1102871,"uid":43718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T04:27:57.000Z","msg":"最近小弟發現Discord佢有個bot可以一路chat一路播歌 <br />\n咁啱小弟喺外國身邊又無咩做 所以想睇下有無巴絲打同我一樣咁啱無咩嘢做 咪入黎傾下計吹下水<br />\n呢個平台傾咩都得 上至天文 下至地理 咩都得<br />\n如果巴絲有心事感情學業工作煩惱都可以係度分享 睇下咁多位巴打有無咩意見畀到你咁<br />\n得閒仲可以點下歌開心share大家音樂既興趣 無聊想廢up下都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最緊要係要禁入嚟睇睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家已經有接近三十個巴絲打喺入面吹緊水啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今晚十二點半左右 小弟會試下開下咪 主題會圍繞心事方面<br />\n有興趣就入嚟聽聽囉<br />\n<a href=\"https://discord.gg/qFTfqpc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdiscord.gg%2FqFTfqpc&d=Cuyai%2BbkQ%2BZKjwazMoctzjQMt3kYY8c646%2Bk6hbI14w%3D&h=bd9a82f3\" target=\"_blank\">https://discord.gg/qFTfqpc</a>"},{"pid":"cdbd517e590ece351cc1b87f033166ce692bbd6b","tid":1102871,"uid":43718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T04:37:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"021049863eeecd8f407a9f865c73d9fb69c3fef1","tid":1102871,"uid":43718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T04:40:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1050d97372c96cbd67215c2888e1e4145275ee7b","tid":1102871,"uid":43718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T04:43:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38efe950a6a43304673bf9a8774d1305e5766254","tid":1102871,"uid":43718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T04:46:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gi